                      Est officiis at quisquam cupiditate ipsa impedit vel quasi? Nulla, dolores fugit
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <span type="button" class="bi bi-flag color-pink" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="left"
                      title="Flagged by John doe, on 12/01/2023 because of this reason. Extra comments: Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit."></span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
